@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@classificationLevelId = {{classificationLevelId}}
@compartmentId = {{compartmentId}}
@compartmentIdAlt = {{compartmentIdAlt}}

### Crear colección — cuerpo válido (nivel + al menos un compartimento)
# Requiere JSON: `name`, `classification_level_id`, `compartment_ids` (lista no vacía).
# Devuelve: 201 y la colección con `classification_level` y `compartments` expandidos.

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Mis expedientes QA",
  "classification_level_id": {{classificationLevelId}},
  "compartment_ids": [{{compartmentId}}]
}

###

### Crear colección — varios compartimentos
# IDs duplicados se deduplican en servidor antes de crear pivotes.

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Paquete multi-cofre",
  "classification_level_id": {{classificationLevelId}},
  "compartment_ids": [{{compartmentId}}, {{compartmentIdAlt}}]
}

###

### Crear colección — nombre con espacios (trim en servidor)

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "  Reviews trimmer  ",
  "classification_level_id": {{classificationLevelId}},
  "compartment_ids": [{{compartmentId}}]
}

###

### Crear colección — `compartment_ids` vacíos (lista vacía prohibida)

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Coleccion invalida empty compartments",
  "classification_level_id": {{classificationLevelId}},
  "compartment_ids": []
}

###

### Crear colección — sin classification_level_id (validación)
# Falta FK obligatorio al crear desde cero si no se usa partial serializer create request.

POST {{host}}/api/v1/document-collections/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Solo texto",
  "compartment_ids": [{{compartmentId}}]
}
